  "html_size": 192981,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110154985491\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110154985491\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54adb2a0ce1e9d7e.png\" width=\"460\" height=\"306\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rheight: 306px; rwidth: 460px\" id=\"20121225_163/isuhani_1356396968556txirB_PNG/20121218_0038011.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54adb2a0ce1e9d7e.png\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">메리크리스마스♬</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">2012년 새해 복 많이 받으시라고 이수한의원 블로그에 포스팅 했던게 엊그제 같은데 벌써 12월 말이네요..</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">한해를 돌아보니 감사하고 행복하고 바쁘게 보냈던 것 같네요.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">그동안 함께 고생해준 이수한의원 식구들을 위해 크리스마스 쿠키를 만들어 보았습니다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">\"콩지의 음식발기\" 블로그 참고했구요.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">그 흔한 과정샷은 없지만...<img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/smarteditor/20121122/emoticon/1_09.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'smarteditor\\/20121122\\/emoticon\\/1_09.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"smarteditor/20121122/emoticon/1_09.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">5시간에 걸쳐 손수 만든거라 뿌듯합니다^^</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/87cc87927e31ea68.jpg\" width=\"353\" height=\"469\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rheight: 469px; rwidth: 353px\" id=\"20121225_119/isuhani_135639965683188sEV_JPEG/20121224_225255.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/87cc87927e31ea68.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">맨 처음 만든<span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"> </span><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #cae37d; COLOR: #000000\">크림치즈 비스켓.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><u><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">재료는</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">박력분 180g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">크림치즈 50g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">포도씨유 20g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">우유 50g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">설탕30g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">소금 1/4t.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">반죽을 &#65279;열심히 쉐킷쉐킷.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">밀대로 밀어서 포크로 구멍 숭숭 뚫어주고 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">오븐이 없음으로 팬에다 구웠답니다^^</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d22b8e42a44d379c.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"498\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rheight: 498px; rwidth: 375px\" id=\"20121225_278/isuhani_13564002766924pF48_JPEG/20121225_005048.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d22b8e42a44d379c.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">다음은 쿠키.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">재료는</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">박력분 200g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">버터 60g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">설탕 80g</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\">계란 한개.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&#65279;열심히 반죽해주고 쿠키커터로 하트모양 뿅뿅 내주고..</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">이것도 역시 </span></span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">오븐이 없어서 팬으로 구워주었어요^^</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">처음엔 아무것도 넣지 않고 굽다가 초코칩도 쏙쏙 넣어서 구웠어요.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">흑설탕을 사용한 관계로 색깔들이 건빵같더라구요..ㅎㅎ</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">역시 쿠키는 식힌다음 먹어야 제맛.<img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/smarteditor/20121122/emoticon/3_32.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'smarteditor\\/20121122\\/emoticon\\/3_32.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"smarteditor/20121122/emoticon/3_32.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a7b4448ce84c9893.jpg\" width=\"513\" height=\"384\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rheight: 384px; rwidth: 513px\" id=\"20121225_264/isuhani_1356400725416nCMQ2_JPEG/20121225_005106.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a7b4448ce84c9893.jpg\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">맛없으면 어쩌나 고민했는데 1차 시식해주신 엄마,아빠가 맛있다고 해주셨어요 ♥_♥</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2b0f5a0923686f7a.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rheight: 430px; rwidth: 574px\" id=\"20121225_269/isuhani_1356400810610FMD0Y_JPEG/20121225_011653.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2b0f5a0923686f7a.jpg\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">이제 식힌다음 포장하기.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">포장이 이쁘지가 않은데 다행히도 이수한의원 선생님들이 기뻐해주시고 맛있다고 해주셔서 만든사람은 많이 기쁩니다^^</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/195fc3743df62044.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 333px; rwidth: 500px\" id=\"20121225_113/isuhani_1356402399912OW9ln_PNG/20121218_0037201.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BFB013')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/195fc3743df62044.png\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">이수한의원 블로그에 들어오시는 여러분 &nbsp;<span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\">MERRY CHRISTMAS~</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">그리고 2013년에는 마음이 따뜻한 한해가 되셨으면 합니다.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ff6c00\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">행복하세요^-^</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401091572\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401091572\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401097142\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401097142\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401099621\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401099621\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401100133\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401100133\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401100805\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401100805\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401100980\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401100980\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401101141\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401101141\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401120692\">&#65279;<span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401124964\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401124964\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401125332\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401125332\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401125572\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401125572\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401125780\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401125780\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1356401126069\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1356401126069\">&#65279;</span></span> </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
